All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
CommandInterface
This class obfuscates the process of sending and validating commands to the robbie app using the MyClient class.
CommandInterface.Coord
Private record class that represents x and y coordinates on a grid
MyClient
This class provides a functionality to interact with an echo server.
MyClient.ClientCallback
The user of this class must implement this callback interface.
Parser
This class is a recursive-descent parser which provides functionality for parsing scripts written in robbie instruction language and interpreting them from instructions into CommandInterface commands to control robbie and the RobbieApp environment.
RobbieInterpreter
This is the class that handles execution of the interpreter program.
Tokenizer
This class provides functionality to break down robbie script files into a stream of keywords and key characters and separates them into individual tokens as an in-between step for interpreting instructions.
